from IPython.display import display, Markdown
values = [
    { "c": 20, "layer": "v0", "t": "2014-01-01" },
    { "c": 10, "layer": "v0", "t": "2014-01-08" },
    { "c": 40, "layer": "v0", "t": "2014-01-15" },
    { "c": 50, "layer": "v0", "t": "2014-01-22" },
    { "c": 70, "layer": "v0", "t": "2014-01-28" },
    { "c": 9, "layer": "v0", "t": "2014-04-02" }
]
spec = {
    "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega-lite/v4.json",
    "data": {
        "values": values
    },
    "encoding": {
        "x": { "field": "t", "type": "temporal" },
        "y": { "field": "c", "type": "quantitative" }
    },
    "mark": { "interpolate": "monotone", "type": "line" }
}

source = [
r"""\
    By looking more closely at the **number of tweets** per day, we 
    can make two observations: first, there are several peaks  days or series of days
    on which the number of tweets is markedly higher than the rest of the year , 
    which correspond to key commemorative moments; and second, a series of two 
    peaks in particular (8 and 9) have a different profile from that of the other peaks.
""",
r"""\
    The peaks observed here vary in type: they may correspond to events concerning all
    the belligerent countries (28 June 2014, centenary of the assassination of Archduke
    Franz Ferdinand); to 11 November  which concerns all the belligerent countries
    but is primarily commemorated in France (3, 5 and 11) and which is also the only
    recurrent event in our database ; to entries into the war (2), mostly dominated
    by the commemoration of the centenary of 4 August 1914, when the United Kingdom
    entered the war; to events concerning a specific group of belligerent countries,
    such as the centenary of the Gallipoli landings, the anniversary of which is now
    Anzac Day, when Australia and New Zealand commemorate the war (4), and the centenary
    of the Easter Rising in Ireland (7); and finally, to the centenary of the
    major battles of 1916 (6 and 8-10).
"""
]

metadata={
    "jdh":{
        "module": "text_object",
        "text": {
            "bootstrapColumLayout": { "md": { "offset":0, "span": 3, "order": 12 } },
            "source": source
        },
        "object": {
            "type": "vega",
            "bootstrapColumLayout": { "md": { "offset": 0, "order": 1, "span": 8 } },
            "component": "TrendLine",
            "cssClassName": [ "bg-white" ],
            "position": "sticky",
            "heightRatio": 0.8,
            "spec": spec,
            "source": [
                "Number of Tweets per day",
            ]
        }
    }
}

display(Markdown(r"".join(steps)), metadata=metadata)
